14#ifndef RDATA_GENERIC_MR_9_C
15#define RDATA_GENERIC_MR_9_C
16
17#define RRTYPE_MR_ATTRIBUTES (0)
18
19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_mr(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21 isc_token_t token;
22 dns_name_t name;
23 isc_buffer_t buffer;
24
25 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
26
27 UNUSED(type);
28 UNUSED(rdclass);
29 UNUSED(callbacks);
30
31 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
32 false));
33
34 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
35 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
36 if (origin == NULL)
37 origin = dns_rootname;
38 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
39 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
40}
41
42static inline isc_result_t
43totext_mr(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
44 isc_region_t region;
45 dns_name_t name;
46 dns_name_t prefix;
47 bool sub;
48
49 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
50 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
51
52 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
53 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
54
55 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
56 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
57
58 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
59
60 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
61}
62
63static inline isc_result_t
64fromwire_mr(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
65 dns_name_t name;
66
67 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
68
69 UNUSED(type);
70 UNUSED(rdclass);
71
72 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
73
74 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
75 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
76}
77
78static inline isc_result_t
79towire_mr(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
80 dns_name_t name;
81 dns_offsets_t offsets;
82 isc_region_t region;
83
84 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
85 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
86
87 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_GLOBAL14);
88
89 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
90 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
91 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
92
93 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
94}
95
96static inline int
97compare_mr(ARGS_COMPARE) {
98 dns_name_t name1;
99 dns_name_t name2;
100 isc_region_t region1;
101 isc_region_t region2;
102
103 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
104 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
105 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
106 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
107 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
108
109 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
110 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
111
112 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
113 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
114
115 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
116 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
117
118 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
119}
120
121static inline isc_result_t
122fromstruct_mr(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
123 dns_rdata_mr_t *mr = source;
124 isc_region_t region;
125
126 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
127 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
128 REQUIRE(mr->common.rdtype == type);
129 REQUIRE(mr->common.rdclass == rdclass);
130
131 UNUSED(type);
132 UNUSED(rdclass);
133
134 dns_name_toregion(&mr->mr, &region);
135 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
136}
137
138static inline isc_result_t
139tostruct_mr(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
140 isc_region_t region;
141 dns_rdata_mr_t *mr = target;
142 dns_name_t name;
143
144 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
145 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
146 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
147
148 mr->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
149 mr->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
150 ISC_LINK_INIT(&mr->common, link);
151
152 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
153 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
154 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
155 dns_name_init(&mr->mr, NULL);
156 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &mr->mr));
157 mr->mctx = mctx;
158 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
159}
160
161static inline void
162freestruct_mr(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
163 dns_rdata_mr_t *mr = source;
164
165 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
166 REQUIRE(mr->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_mr);
167
168 if (mr->mctx == NULL)
169 return;
170 dns_name_free(&mr->mr, mr->mctx);
171 mr->mctx = NULL;
172}
173
174static inline isc_result_t
175additionaldata_mr(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
176 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
177
178 UNUSED(rdata);
179 UNUSED(add);
180 UNUSED(arg);
181
182 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
183}
184
185static inline isc_result_t
186digest_mr(ARGS_DIGEST) {
187 isc_region_t r;
188 dns_name_t name;
189
190 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
191
192 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
193 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
194 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
195
196 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
197}
198
199static inline bool
200checkowner_mr(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
201
202 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
203
204 UNUSED(name);
205 UNUSED(type);
206 UNUSED(rdclass);
207 UNUSED(wildcard);
208
209 return (true);
210}
211
212static inline bool
213checknames_mr(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
214
215 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_mr);
216
217 UNUSED(rdata);
218 UNUSED(owner);
219 UNUSED(bad);
220
221 return (true);
222}
223
224static inline int
225casecompare_mr(ARGS_COMPARE) {
226 return (compare_mr(rdata1, rdata2));
227}
